description: We are proud to introduce one of the finest brick 3 bedroom duplex homes in the Mill Basin area.  As you enter there are hardwood floors that glisten leading into the spacious living room and formal dining room.  The kitchen has updated stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops and mitsubishi ductless split system.  There is a convenient powder room on this level as well.  The top floor features 3 large bedrooms, updated bathroom featuring European tile.  The basement is a full finished area with a separate entrance set up as a great room, and den/office.  The backyard was recently updated with pavers and space for family gatherings.  The home has updated mechanicals; private drive and built in garage.
